CAREER STATISTICS AND CAREER HIGHS

2012: Enters into her sophomore season with the Spartan squad . . . is a solid technical player . . . will start in the Spartan attack this season either in the central midfield or up front . . . will get the chance to gain more quality experience while putting up results this season.

2011: Appeared in 17 games this season with 15 starts . . . finished the season with two points . . . scored one goal and had a single-game high six shots during a 4-1 win over Wesley on Oct. 1.
